              <div class="wpb_wrapper">
               <h1 style="text-align: left; color: #ffffff; font-size: 34px; line-height: 50px; font-weight: 500;">
                Enterprise Python, Perl &amp; Tcl
               </h1>
              </div>
             </div>
             <div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element cesis_text_transform_none vc_custom_1611148500335" style=" font-size:20px; line-height:32px; ">
              <div class="wpb_wrapper">
               <p style="text-align: left; color: #ffffff; font-family: 'Open Sans';">
                <strong>
                 Get the most from your use of Perl, Python or Tcl and reduce your compliance, legal, and security risks.
                </strong>
                <br/>
                We offer custom managed and self-serve distributions, including support and maintenance, on Windows, Linux, AIX and more – even for 32-bit and older releases.
               </p>
              </div>
             </div>
